asset_data.short_desc: Known as a run-churning machine, there have been nine instances in Virat Kohli’s Test career which he would want to forget.
asset_data.asset_title: The rare blips in Virat Kohli’s impressive Test career

asset_data.short_desc: In eleven years, Kohli has recorded 68 international centuries, including 27 in the last three years alone.
Another jam-packed week is almost upon us, and while you’re aware of Steve Smith and Virat Kohli’s achievements, we’re sure you have missed these happenings.
asset_data.asset_title: Things you might have missed this week

asset_data.short_desc: Virat Kohli beat Javed Miandad to become the highest run-scorer against West Indies in ODIs.
asset_data.asset_title: Virat Kohli underlines his supremacy against West Indies

asset_data.short_desc: The trio of Virat Kohli, Jasprit Bumrah and KL Rahul performing well would be crucial for India to continue their unbeaten record against Pakistan at World Cups.
asset_data.asset_title: Key Players: Kohli and Rahul hold the key for India against Pakistan

asset_data.short_desc: A sixth consecutive defeat in the ongoing Indian T20 League has put Team Bengaluru’s status in massive jeopardy. More than that, Virat Kohli’s repute of being a leader is under serious threat.
asset_data.asset_title: Where does skipper Virat Kohli stand among Indian T20 League elite?

asset_data.short_desc: Virat Kohli’s Team Bengaluru are the only side amongst the lot who are yet to win an Indian T20 League game this season. Having kickstarted their campaign on a losing note against the defending champions Chennai, Bengaluru slumped to defeat in their next three fixtures.
asset_data.asset_title: Top picks for the Bengaluru vs Kolkata tie
